&#x671D;&#x4F1F;&#x3001;&#x91D1;&#x57CE;&#x6B66;&#x8FD9;&#x6837;&#x7684;&#x5927;&#x5496;&#x81F3;&#x5C11;&#x4E5F;&#x8BE5;&#x662F;&#x90E8;&#x4FDD;&#x6301;&#x4EE5;&#x5F80;&#x6C34;&#x51C6;&#x7684;&#x7535;&#x5F71;&#x3002;&#x6700;&#x540E;&#xFF0C;&#x6881;&#x671D;&#x4F1F;&#x7684;&#x773C;&#x775B;&#x4F1A;&#x8BF4;&#x8BDD;&#xFF0C;&#x91D1;&#x57CE;&#x6B66;&#x7684;&#x58F0;&#x97F3;&#x6709;&#x6545;&#x4E8B;&#xFF0C;&#x51B2;&#x7740;&#x4ED6;&#x4EEC;&#x4FE9;&#x6211;&#x7ED9;&#x7535;&#x5F71;&#x4E24;&#x9897;&#x661F;&#xFF0C;&#x5F53;&#x7136;&#x6EE1;&#x5206;&#x662F;&#x4E94;&#x661F;&#xFF1A;&#xFF09;</span></span></p><p><br></p><p></p>\r\n			<!-- <p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">有网友在调侃说，2016年是国内大导演集体扑街的一年，远有冯小刚导演的《我不是潘金莲》遭遇票房和影评滑铁卢，近有张艺谋导演《长城》票房和影评的两极分化。在这不甘寂寞的12月里，于14年就立项的《摆渡人》上映了，号称打磨了三年的剧本，集结了</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(249, 110, 87);\">梁朝伟</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">、</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(249, 110, 87);\">金城武</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">、</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(249, 110, 87);\">陈奕迅</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这样的男神阵容，有杜鹃、张榕容这类有口碑的青年演员，还有大名鼎鼎的墨镜王担当编剧，就算影片演员还有杨颖，总不至于是部烂片吧？但是当影片海报出现，当网友们看完了预告的第一秒，都炸开锅了。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"/Uploads/image/20161229/16093433733.jpg\" title=\"16093433733.jpg\" alt=\"640.webp.jpg\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">大IP改编电影在这两年的院线里并不少见，影片未上映前就有一大票粉丝翘首以盼，</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如何把握观众和粉丝之间的观影体验是个大难题</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">。导演张嘉佳的《从你的全世界路过》火遍了各大书单，文青们几乎张口就来一句“我希望有个如你一般的人，像古城里温暖的阳光，山间的清泉...”。但是这样深情的短篇故事，改编成如此荒诞的喜剧片，怕是对原著粉们冲击不小。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"/Uploads/image/20161229/16093508524.jpg\" title=\"16093508524.jpg\" alt=\"640.webp (1).jpg\"/></span></span></p><section class=\"\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">下文包含轻微剧透，谨慎阅读</strong></span></p></section></section></section><p></p><section class=\"\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p></section></section></section><section class=\"\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">影片里充斥着好几个光怪陆离的主线故事，陈末与何木子，管春和毛毛，马力和小玉，莫名其妙需要摆渡的小太妹李宇春、新郎逃婚却痴痴等的贾玲。主线故事的展开让人觉得莫名其妙，虽然看得懂但因为一句激将法就把一个女生追到手的荒诞故事并不是观众们所要看的梁朝伟和杜鹃。金城武饰演的管春和张榕容饰演的毛毛大概是影评里最正常的一对，青春年少因为街头游戏机而展开的懵懂爱情，到了三五年后为了挽回而又努力付出帮助毛毛找回曾经的记忆，和近些年的青春爱情片剧本一模一样！至于年轻时是鹿晗长大后成了陈奕迅的马力，以及他的脑残粉小玉的故事，预告片里梁朝伟说的那句”好大一轮备胎“已经说明了这个故事。</p></section></section></section><p></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/Uploads/image/20161229/16093534800.jpg\" title=\"16093534800.jpg\" alt=\"640.webp (2).jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(7, 7, 7); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">影片的多数画面都显得凌乱而尴尬，酒吧的灯红酒绿、五颜六色的灯光打在角色的脸上，还有旁白不时来一句鸡汤，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(249, 110, 87);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">”每个人心里都有脆弱的一面，如果放大这种脆弱的话，没人想活“、”人跟人之间的安全距离是一百二十二公分，跟你喜欢的人在一起，你会努力去缩短这距离“<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(7, 7, 7);\"></span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(7, 7, 7);\">。还有打着情怀牌的配乐虽然很有代入感，但是一会儿是beyond的《喜欢你》，一会儿又是灌篮高手的《好像大声说爱你》真的是一锅东北大乱炖。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(7, 7, 7); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(249, 110, 87);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(7, 7, 7);\">这部影片在网上正在遭受口碑的两级分化，其实对于非科班出身第一次执导的张嘉佳，无非是我们的期望太高了，觉得有王家卫和梁朝伟、金城武这样的大咖至少也该是部保持以往水准的电影。最后，梁朝伟的眼睛会说话，金城武的声音有故事，冲着他们俩我给电影两颗星，当然满分是五星：）</span></span></p><p><br/></p> -->\r\n		', '1', '', null, '0', '《摆渡人 》影评：男神演技下线是什么体验', 'http://www.51oscar.com/Uploads/Movie/Poster/58578ee5f2e9e.jpg', 'http://www.51oscar.com/Public/Home/images/touxiang_18.jpg', null);
